---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About GlowPicked - AI-Powered Beauty Reviews"
  description="Learn about GlowPicked's AI-powered approach to luxury beauty and skincare reviews. Discover how we analyze thousands of products to bring you unbiased, data-driven recommendations."
  keywords="about glowpicked, ai beauty reviews, luxury skincare analysis, beauty product testing, ai-powered recommendations"
>
  <article class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header">
        <div class="header-content">
          <h1>About GlowPicked</h1>
          <p class="tagline">Where AI Meets Beauty Intelligence</p>
          <p class="intro">
            We're revolutionizing how you discover and evaluate luxury beauty products. 
            Using cutting-edge AI technology, we analyze thousands of products, ingredients, 
            and real user experiences to bring you the most honest, comprehensive beauty reviews.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-visual">
          <div class="ai-beauty-icon">
            <span class="icon">‚ú®</span>
            <span class="ai-badge">AI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="our-mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="mission-content">
          <div class="mission-text">
            <p>
              The beauty industry is overwhelming. With thousands of products launched every year, 
              conflicting reviews, and marketing noise, finding products that truly work can feel impossible.
            </p>
            <p>
              That's where we come in. GlowPicked harnesses the power of artificial intelligence to 
              cut through the noise and deliver insights you can trust. Our AI aggregates thousands 
              of real customer reviews, cross-references ingredient databases and scientific studies, 
              and synthesizes real user experiences into clear, actionable recommendations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">Thousands</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Reviews Analyzed</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">Multi-Platform</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Data Sources</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">AI-Powered</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Analysis</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="how-we-work">
        <h2>How Our AI Works</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Our proprietary AI system combines multiple analysis layers to give you the complete picture:
        </p>
        
        <div class="analysis-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üî¨</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Ingredient Analysis</h3>
              <p>
                We analyze every ingredient in detail, cross-referencing scientific literature 
                to understand efficacy, safety, and potential interactions. Our AI understands 
                not just what's in the product, but how ingredients work together.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üìä</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Review Synthesis</h3>
              <p>
                Our AI processes thousands of real user reviews from multiple platforms, 
                filtering out fake reviews and identifying genuine patterns in user experiences. 
                We understand context, skin types, and usage patterns.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üèÜ</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Performance Scoring</h3>
              <p>
                Using our proprietary scoring algorithm, we rate products across multiple 
                dimensions: effectiveness, value, ingredient quality, user satisfaction, 
                and safety. Every score is backed by data.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">üí°</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Personalized Recommendations</h3>
              <p>
                Our AI learns from your preferences, skin concerns, and budget to provide 
                increasingly personalized recommendations. The more you engage, the smarter 
                our suggestions become.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="what-makes-us-different">
        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <div class="differentiators">
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üö´</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>No Bias, Just Data</h3>
              <p>
                Unlike traditional reviewers who might be influenced by brand relationships, 
                our AI evaluates products purely on merit. We have no favorite brands ‚Äî 
                only favorite results.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Real-Time Analysis</h3>
              <p>
                Our AI continuously monitors new products, updated formulations, and emerging 
                user feedback. Our recommendations evolve as new data becomes available.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üîç</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Comprehensive Coverage</h3>
              <p>
                We don't just focus on popular products. Our AI discovers hidden gems, 
                analyzes indie brands, and evaluates everything from drugstore finds 
                to luxury splurges.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon">üéØ</div>
            <div class="diff-content">
              <h3>Context-Aware Reviews</h3>
              <p>
                Our AI understands that what works for dry skin might not work for oily skin, 
                and what's worth it at $20 might not be at $200. Every recommendation 
                considers your specific context.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="our-values">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üî¨ Science-First</h3>
            <p>
              Every claim we make is backed by scientific research. We believe in evidence-based 
              beauty recommendations that you can trust.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üåü Transparency</h3>
            <p>
              We're open about our methodology, our AI's limitations, and our affiliate 
              partnerships. No hidden agendas, just honest insights.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üíö Sustainability</h3>
            <p>
              We factor environmental impact into our recommendations, highlighting brands 
              that prioritize sustainable practices and packaging.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>ü§ù Inclusivity</h3>
            <p>
              Beauty is for everyone. Our AI evaluates products across all skin tones, 
              types, and concerns to ensure inclusive recommendations.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>üìö Education</h3>
            <p>
              We don't just tell you what to buy ‚Äî we help you understand why. 
              Our goal is to make you a more informed beauty consumer.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value">
            <h3>‚ö° Innovation</h3>
            <p>
              We continuously improve our AI algorithms and explore new ways to help you 
              discover your perfect beauty routine.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="team-section">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">
          GlowPicked is an independent, AI-powered beauty review platform. We're a small team 
          that leverages advanced AI technology to do what no single human reviewer could: 
          analyze thousands of real customer reviews, ingredient databases, and expert opinions simultaneously.
        </p>
        
        <div class="team-highlights">
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>AI-Powered Analysis</h3>
            <p>
              Our AI systems specialize in natural language processing and data analysis, 
              synthesizing thousands of real human reviews into actionable insights.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>Data-Driven Approach</h3>
            <p>
              We cross-reference ingredient databases, scientific literature, and real user 
              experiences to ensure our recommendations are accurate and evidence-based.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="team-item">
            <h3>Transparency First</h3>
            <p>
              We're upfront about what we are: an AI-powered platform, not human testers. 
              Our strength is aggregating thousands of real experiences ‚Äî not pretending to be something we're not.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="transparency-section">
        <h2>Transparency & Trust</h2>
        <div class="transparency-content">
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>How We Make Money</h3>
            <p>
              We earn commissions when you purchase products through our affiliate links. 
              This doesn't influence our reviews ‚Äî our AI evaluates products independently, 
              and we clearly disclose all affiliate relationships.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>Our AI's Limitations</h3>
            <p>
              While our AI is sophisticated, it's not perfect. We can't replace professional 
              dermatological advice, and individual results may vary. We're constantly 
              working to improve our algorithms' accuracy and coverage.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="transparency-item">
            <h3>Data Privacy</h3>
            <p>
              We take your privacy seriously. We don't sell personal data, and we use 
              aggregated, anonymized information to improve our recommendations. 
              See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="future-vision">
        <h2>The Future of Beauty Intelligence</h2>
        <div class="vision-content">
          <p>
            We're just getting started. Our roadmap includes personalized skincare routines, 
            virtual try-on technology, ingredient interaction analysis, and partnerships 
            with beauty brands to create truly effective products based on our AI insights.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We believe the future of beauty is intelligent, personalized, and transparent. 
            Join us as we transform how the world discovers and experiences beauty products.
          </p>
          
          <div class="cta-section">
            <h3>Ready to Experience AI-Powered Beauty?</h3>
            <p>Start exploring our reviews and discover your next holy grail product.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
              <a href="/" class="cta-primary">Explore Reviews</a>
              <a href="mailto:contact@glowpicked.com" class="cta-secondary">Get In Touch</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-light) 0%, white 100%);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .header-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .header-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-beauty-icon {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .ai-beauty-icon .icon {
    font-size: 5rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3));
  }

  .ai-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .our-mission {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .our-mission h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mission-stats {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .stat:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .how-we-work {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .how-we-work h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .analysis-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .what-makes-us-different {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .what-makes-us-different h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .differentiators {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .diff-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .diff-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .diff-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .diff-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .diff-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .our-values {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .our-values h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .value h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .value p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .team-section,
  .transparency-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .team-section h2,
  .transparency-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .team-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .team-item {
    background: var(--text);
    color: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .team-item p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .transparency-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .transparency-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .transparency-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .transparency-item p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .transparency-item a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .transparency-item a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .future-vision {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .future-vision h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .cta-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 150px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-light);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .mission-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .mission-stats {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .header-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .ai-beauty-icon {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .ai-beauty-icon .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }

    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .diff-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-primary,
    .cta-secondary {
      width: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>